comment.body:
@JunyeongSeok just a quick note, the issue is not blocking, for some reason the recursive resolver in Hong Kong fails to resolve naver domains.

My guess is that it only fails to resolve it when the DNS query contains a specific EDNS Client Subnet.

In order to reproduce it we'll need to know the /24 subnet of a user who can reproduce it now.

@piquark6046 if you are able to reproduce the issue please share your current /24 subnet (your IP address with the last part replaced by 0).
